<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <title>Welcome to Smart LMS</title>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  <style type="text/css">
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', 'Open Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #E5E5E5;
    }
    table, td {
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .container {
      width: 600px;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: auto;
    }
    .header {
      position: relative;
      height: 130px;
      background: #2859A5;
      border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .header-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100%;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .header-icon {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .header-title {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .header-desc {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #e7eef7;
      margin-top: 4px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .header-wave {
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 36px;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .subtitle {
      display: block;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #357AE8;
      margin-top: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1px;
    }
    .main-content {
      padding: 48px 30px 40px;
      background: #fff;
      color: #000;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 24px rgba(44, 94, 209, 0.03);
    }
    .main-content h1 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 8px 0;
      color: #222;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    .main-content .subtitle {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #357AE8;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }
    .main-content p {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin: 0 0 16px 0;
    }
    .highlight, b, strong {
      color: #4C83EE;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100%;
      background: #4C83EE;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 0;
      color: #fff !important;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 21px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      border-radius: 7px;
      margin: 16px 0 24px 0;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #3773d7;
    }
    .divider {
      width: 120px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #E3E9EF;
      margin: 32px auto 24px;
      display: block;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 24px 0 48px 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #8B949F;
      text-align: center;
      background: #F6FAFB;
      border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4C83EE;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    @media only screen and (max-width:595px) {
      .container {
        width: 100% !important;
      }
      .main-content {
        padding: 32px 12px 30px;
      }
      .header-title {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .header-desc {
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .header-content {
        gap: 8px;
      }
      .subtitle {
        font-size: 13px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center" bgcolor="#E5E5E5">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table class="container" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
          <tr>
            <td class="header">
              <div class="header-content">
                <!-- Graduation Cap SVG Icon -->
                <span class="header-icon">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" width="42" height="42" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M24 8L44 17L24 26L4 17L24 8Z" fill="#fff" fill-opacity="0.21"/>
                    <path d="M44 17V23M44 23L24 32L4 23M44 23V31L24 40L4 31V23" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <div class="header-title">Smart LMS</div>
                  <div class="header-desc">Smart Learning Management System</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <!-- Lower, gentler SVG wave -->
              <svg class="header-wave" viewBox="0 0 600 36" width="600" height="36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
                <path d="M0 18C100 30 200 30 300 18C400 6 500 6 600 18V36H0V18Z" fill="#fff" fill-opacity="0.93"/>
              </svg>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="main-content">
              <h1>Welcome to Smart LMS!</h1>
              <div class="subtitle">Your learning journey starts here</div>
              <p>Hello <b>{{username}}</b>,</p>
              <p>We're excited to welcome you to the <b>Smart Learning Management System</b>. Your account has been created successfully, and you're now ready to begin your learning journey.</p>
              <a class="button" href="{{loginUrl}}" title="Access Your Account"><b>Access Your Account</b></a>
              <p>Our platform provides all the tools you need to excel in your educational journey. If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
              <span class="divider"></span>
              <p><strong>Best regards,</strong><br><strong>Wilfierd Smart LMS Team</strong></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="footer">
              Wilfierd Smart LMS Inc.<br>
              123 Academic Way, Campus City, EduState, 99999<br>
              <a href="https://wilfierdsmartlms.systems">wilfierdsmartlms.systems</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>